1
00:00:00,640 --> 00:00:04,440
<font size="20">{\an8}<font face="Comic Sans MS"><b><font color="#2b291e">Nasu Oyaji Curry</font></b></font></font>

2
00:00:06,140 --> 00:00:08,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The Kobe trip ended safely.</i></font>

3
00:00:09,110 --> 00:00:10,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And summer break
was nearing its end.</i></font>

4
00:00:12,340 --> 00:00:13,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Casual clothes.</i></font>

5
00:00:13,950 --> 00:00:17,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Chinatown. Sun parasol and pizza.</i></font>

6
00:00:18,500 --> 00:00:20,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The aquarium...</i></font>

7
00:00:20,910 --> 00:00:23,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The scent of Senpai's shampoo...</i></font>

8
00:00:24,610 --> 00:00:28,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Holding hands, and having fun.</i></font>

9
00:00:31,950 --> 00:00:34,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>More and more, it's becoming not enough...</i></font>

10
00:00:34,430 --> 00:00:36,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yoi! Yoi!</font>

11
00:00:37,140 --> 00:00:38,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yoi!</font>

12
00:00:38,180 --> 00:00:39,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The rice! The rice!</font>

13
00:00:39,850 --> 00:00:40,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh!</font>

14
00:00:44,580 --> 00:00:46,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The rice...</font>

15
00:02:16,590 --> 00:02:18,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, man...</font>

16
00:02:19,450 --> 00:02:21,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's surprisingly slow today.</font>

17
00:02:22,340 --> 00:02:26,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe I should ask Asami to 
bring her college friends over.</font>

18
00:02:26,790 --> 00:02:29,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think Sis would be pissed.</font>

19
00:02:29,010 --> 00:02:30,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yep, I know.</font>

20
00:02:30,980 --> 00:02:33,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, how about the kids 
at your school, Yoi?</font>

21
00:02:33,100 --> 00:02:35,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know! That boy...</font>

22
00:02:36,740 --> 00:02:38,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The curry fanatic!</font>

23
00:02:38,720 --> 00:02:41,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Oh, him.</i></font>

24
00:02:41,540 --> 00:02:43,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm the curry fanatic!</i></font>

25
00:02:44,470 --> 00:02:46,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Business sure is slow.</font>

26
00:02:47,620 --> 00:02:51,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I haven't seen Senpai
since the Kobe trip.</i></font>

27
00:02:52,010 --> 00:02:54,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I've been busy with this and that...</i></font>

28
00:02:55,810 --> 00:02:57,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If I'd known this would happen,</i></font>

29
00:02:57,010 --> 00:02:59,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I would have kept my schedule 
open a little more...</i></font>

30
00:03:01,830 --> 00:03:03,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Welcome...</font>

31
00:03:03,710 --> 00:03:04,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yo.</font>

32
00:03:05,670 --> 00:03:06,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Senpai?!</font>

33
00:03:07,830 --> 00:03:09,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What brought this on?</font>

34
00:03:09,720 --> 00:03:12,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just came by to eat curry.</font>

35
00:03:12,810 --> 00:03:14,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can I sit anywhere?</font>

36
00:03:14,120 --> 00:03:15,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, please, go ahead.</font>

37
00:03:19,080 --> 00:03:23,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, I'd like one special. Large.</font>

38
00:03:25,510 --> 00:03:28,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Oh, he really did just 
come here for curry.</i></font>

39
00:03:25,730 --> 00:03:28,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Uh, and for my drink...</font>

40
00:03:28,980 --> 00:03:30,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}iced coffee.</font>

41
00:03:30,480 --> 00:03:31,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Welcome.</font>

42
00:03:31,720 --> 00:03:32,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh!</font>

43
00:03:32,770 --> 00:03:33,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello.</font>

44
00:03:34,060 --> 00:03:35,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oji-kun.</font>

45
00:03:36,510 --> 00:03:40,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was passing by, so I figured 
I'd stop by for dinner.</font>

46
00:03:40,010 --> 00:03:42,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, come in and eat.</font>

47
00:03:44,020 --> 00:03:45,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello.</font>

48
00:03:47,580 --> 00:03:48,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hello.</font>

49
00:03:55,460 --> 00:03:57,420
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="24"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b><font color="#321f23">Nasu Oyaji Curry</font></b></font></font></font>

50
00:03:57,810 --> 00:03:59,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks for the grub.</font>

51
00:04:02,770 --> 00:04:04,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yoi, can you handle the register?</font>

52
00:04:04,370 --> 00:04:05,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, yeah.</font>

53
00:04:05,870 --> 00:04:07,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">One moment, please.</font>

54
00:04:08,470 --> 00:04:11,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, one large special. 
And the drink was...</font>

55
00:04:11,430 --> 00:04:13,890
<font size="20">{\an8}<font face="Comic Sans MS"><b><font color="#7a6667">Nasu <font color="#a2867e">Oyaji <font color="#c09790">Curry</font></font></font></b></font></font>

56
00:04:12,840 --> 00:04:13,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you for coming!</font>

57
00:04:14,220 --> 00:04:16,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was real good as always.</font>

58
00:04:17,340 --> 00:04:19,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's been a while since I've 
had something nourishing.</font>

59
00:04:19,800 --> 00:04:21,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm glad to hear that.</font>

60
00:04:21,000 --> 00:04:22,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You keep eating from
the convenience store...</font>

61
00:04:23,270 --> 00:04:25,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't you ever go back 
to your parents' house to eat?</font>

62
00:04:26,240 --> 00:04:29,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? No way. It's a pain.</font>

63
00:04:29,460 --> 00:04:32,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Besides, don't you ever get the 
urge to eat junk food for dinner?</font>

64
00:04:32,890 --> 00:04:34,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like burgers and takoyaki.</font>

65
00:04:34,750 --> 00:04:36,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, takoyaki... That's true.</font>

66
00:04:36,810 --> 00:04:39,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd like to eat a whole bunch for dinner.</font>

67
00:04:39,740 --> 00:04:41,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I wonder how many I could eat.</font>

68
00:04:39,970 --> 00:04:42,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you imagining right now?</font>

69
00:04:41,010 --> 00:04:42,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Maybe ten?</font>

70
00:04:42,810 --> 00:04:44,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Burgers are good, too.</font>

71
00:04:44,840 --> 00:04:47,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh... a takoyaki burger...</font>

72
00:04:48,260 --> 00:04:50,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then, wanna have a takoyaki party
 date sometime?</font>

73
00:04:51,930 --> 00:04:52,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At my place.</font>

74
00:04:53,940 --> 00:04:54,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>His place?</i></font>

75
00:04:58,050 --> 00:05:00,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, don't freeze up on me now.</font>

76
00:05:00,250 --> 00:05:03,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-Is that what this was leading to?!</font>

77
00:05:03,720 --> 00:05:06,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought we were just making 
small talk after the curry!</font>

78
00:05:05,860 --> 00:05:06,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Y'know...</font>

79
00:05:07,160 --> 00:05:10,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can't you stop, think, and realize
 that I came to see you?</font>

80
00:05:12,120 --> 00:05:15,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For the record, I <i>am</i> inviting you over.</font>

81
00:05:21,740 --> 00:05:25,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh... Um... I-If...</font>

82
00:05:26,260 --> 00:05:28,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If my schedule frees up, 
I'll think about it.</font>

83
00:05:30,220 --> 00:05:33,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, come on. Let's be 
a little more proactive here.</font>

84
00:05:33,250 --> 00:05:35,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I have work and other things...</font>

85
00:05:43,110 --> 00:05:45,570
<font size="20">{\an8}<b><font size="10"><font color="#b3c6bf">Nobara-chan</font></font></b></font>

86
00:05:46,210 --> 00:05:47,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nobara-chan!</font>

87
00:05:47,700 --> 00:05:48,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you finish your homework?!</font>

88
00:05:51,710 --> 00:05:52,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not yet.</font>

89
00:05:53,370 --> 00:05:55,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Oh, good! Me neither!</i></font>

90
00:05:55,860 --> 00:05:57,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Do you think Yoi-chan got it done?</i></font>

91
00:05:57,980 --> 00:06:00,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Prince? I'm sure she did.</font>

92
00:06:01,130 --> 00:06:03,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right! Yoi-chan-sama would!</font>

93
00:06:03,900 --> 00:06:05,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">By the way, about Yoi-chan.</font>

94
00:06:05,820 --> 00:06:07,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't you think she seemed like</font>

95
00:06:07,340 --> 00:06:10,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">she was getting along with Senpai 
real well when we were in Kobe?</font>

96
00:06:10,050 --> 00:06:11,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I know, right?</font>

97
00:06:11,260 --> 00:06:14,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She just might be meeting 
up with Senpai as we speak...</font>

98
00:06:18,260 --> 00:06:20,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you very much!</font>

99
00:06:21,080 --> 00:06:22,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, hey!</font>

100
00:06:23,780 --> 00:06:24,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yo!</font>

101
00:06:30,660 --> 00:06:33,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are things with the Prince going well?</font>

102
00:06:35,190 --> 00:06:37,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're such a pain.</font>

103
00:06:37,810 --> 00:06:38,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, but...</font>

104
00:06:39,610 --> 00:06:42,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was wondering whatever 
happened to that dude.</font>

105
00:06:42,630 --> 00:06:46,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y'know, the part-timer?
The handsome guy.</font>

106
00:06:46,380 --> 00:06:50,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, beats me.
I think he still works there?</font>

107
00:06:51,100 --> 00:06:52,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't know, though.</font>

108
00:06:53,430 --> 00:06:54,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh-huh...</font>

109
00:06:56,170 --> 00:06:57,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

110
00:06:57,020 --> 00:06:58,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, it's just...</font>

111
00:06:59,570 --> 00:07:03,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That guy seemed like he had 
his eyes on the Prince.</font>

112
00:07:04,180 --> 00:07:07,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like they had some real 
chemistry, or something.</font>

113
00:07:08,490 --> 00:07:11,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I might just be 
overthinking it, but...</font>

114
00:07:11,380 --> 00:07:12,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kuwa...</font>

115
00:07:12,260 --> 00:07:12,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm?</font>

116
00:07:13,220 --> 00:07:15,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't drop weird hints at me, man.</font>

117
00:07:16,450 --> 00:07:19,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My bad. My bad.
Don't take it seriously.</font>

118
00:07:19,260 --> 00:07:23,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">First of all, there's no way anything 
like that would happen with Yoi-chan.</font>

119
00:07:23,690 --> 00:07:25,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, true.</font>

120
00:07:25,230 --> 00:07:27,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But what if something <i>were</i> to...</font>

121
00:07:28,940 --> 00:07:31,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kuwa! Why, you!</font>

122
00:07:31,080 --> 00:07:33,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My bad, my bad! I'm kiddin'! I'm kiddin'!</font>

123
00:07:33,260 --> 00:07:35,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why ya little... Take that! And that!</font>

124
00:07:35,360 --> 00:07:37,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, stop that!</font>

125
00:07:37,910 --> 00:07:39,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At my place...</font>

126
00:07:40,290 --> 00:07:44,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yoi-chan, Yoi-chan, Yoi-chan-sensei!</font>

127
00:07:44,750 --> 00:07:45,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

128
00:07:45,390 --> 00:07:46,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We solved the problem.</font>

129
00:07:47,380 --> 00:07:51,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Oh, then you think you 
could solve this next one?</font>

130
00:07:51,900 --> 00:07:56,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}For this problem, you apply this part of
 the problem we just did, and...</font>

131
00:07:52,980 --> 00:07:55,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If we're going to be at
 his house alone together...</i></font>

132
00:07:55,740 --> 00:07:58,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Are we going to kiss... and stuff?</i></font>

133
00:07:56,010 --> 00:07:59,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Oh, yeah, yeah. That's it.</font>

134
00:08:03,620 --> 00:08:07,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No, we're there to have takoyaki! Yep!</i></font>

135
00:08:08,150 --> 00:08:10,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sensei's weird today.</font>

136
00:08:10,600 --> 00:08:11,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

137
00:08:13,740 --> 00:08:15,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can't picture it.</i></font>

138
00:08:16,230 --> 00:08:17,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I wonder what it's like...</i></font>

139
00:08:20,280 --> 00:08:21,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No!</i></font>

140
00:08:21,090 --> 00:08:22,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Like I said, we're there 
to have takoyaki...!</i></font>

141
00:08:24,030 --> 00:08:27,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Besides, it's not like my schedule is 
going to conveniently free up anyway.</i></font>

142
00:08:36,410 --> 00:08:38,370
<font size="20">{\an8}<b><font size="14"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#fef9fd">Nasu Oyaji Curry</font></font></font></b></font>

143
00:08:38,370 --> 00:08:40,330
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="15"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><b><font color="#a9c3cd">We apologize for the inconvenience,
but we will be temporarily closed today.</font></b></font></font></font>

144
00:08:38,370 --> 00:08:40,330
<font size="20">{\an8}<font color="#947764">m 0 0 l 220 0 220 16 0 16</font></font>

145
00:08:40,770 --> 00:08:43,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I got it!</font>

146
00:08:43,290 --> 00:08:46,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? What did you get? 
A winning lottery ticket?</font>

147
00:08:46,680 --> 00:08:48,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No! I got food poisoning!</font>

148
00:08:48,700 --> 00:08:52,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Was it the meal set I had for lunch?</font>

149
00:08:52,260 --> 00:08:56,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For now, I'm going to the hospital, 
so close up the shop for me!</font>

150
00:08:56,940 --> 00:08:59,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You two can take today off!</font>

151
00:08:59,730 --> 00:09:03,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Make sure you lock the doors 
and turn off the gas and lights!</font>

152
00:09:05,470 --> 00:09:09,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess we'll close up shop 
and go home for today.</font>

153
00:09:09,130 --> 00:09:10,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

154
00:09:12,280 --> 00:09:15,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My schedule... is freed up.</i></font>

155
00:09:16,840 --> 00:09:19,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If my schedule frees up, 
I'll think about it.</font>

156
00:09:19,660 --> 00:09:25,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Since I was the one who said that, I 
should be the one to contact him... right?</i></font>

157
00:09:25,780 --> 00:09:28,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But if I do that...</i></font>

158
00:09:28,060 --> 00:09:29,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um.</font>

159
00:09:31,910 --> 00:09:35,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you have some free time right now?</font>

160
00:09:41,260 --> 00:09:43,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry for putting you through this.</font>

161
00:09:43,480 --> 00:09:47,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No worries. They put my dad on an 
IV drip so he's all right now.</font>

162
00:09:48,450 --> 00:09:52,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I did promise to help you pick 
out a present for your sister.</font>

163
00:09:52,710 --> 00:09:53,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry.</font>

164
00:09:54,280 --> 00:09:55,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Well, I guess it can't be helped.</i></font>

165
00:09:55,640 --> 00:09:57,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll meet with Senpai another time.</i></font>

166
00:09:58,390 --> 00:10:01,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">By the way, how old is 
your younger sister?</font>

167
00:10:01,610 --> 00:10:02,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She's in third grade.</font>

168
00:10:02,650 --> 00:10:04,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Third grade, huh?</font>

169
00:10:04,490 --> 00:10:06,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder what she'd like.</font>

170
00:10:06,510 --> 00:10:10,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What did you want at that age, Yoi-san?</font>

171
00:10:10,730 --> 00:10:15,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um... I was taking karate back then, 
so something like a sports bottle.</font>

172
00:10:15,230 --> 00:10:17,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or a face towel. 
That would make me really happy.</font>

173
00:10:17,920 --> 00:10:19,890
